<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('../partials/head', {title: 'Home'}) -%>
</head>
<body>
  <main role="main">
    <%- include('../partials/header') -%>

    <section class="banners">
      <div class="img-slider">
        <div><img src="https://static.bannerstack.com/img/index-banner-01.jpg" alt="Your Choice"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="yellow-title">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="column">
          <h3>WELCOME TO THE FUTURE OF WIDE-FORMAT</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="column">
            <a href="#" class="centered-img-block"><img src="https://static.bannerstack.com/img/index-flash-sale-01.jpg" alt="Flash Sale"></a>
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <div class="info-teaser">
              <a href="#"><img src="https://static.bannerstack.com/img/index-material.jpg" alt=""></a>
              <p>
                <strong>HIGH-QUALITY MATERIAL</strong><br>
                No matter what material you choose we'll ensure that you have the highest quality final product
                possible. Our production team makes sure that everything from printing to shipping is handled with
                the utmost care. BannerStack is here to get it right the first time.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-teaser">
              <a href="#"><img src="https://static.bannerstack.com/img/index-color.jpg" alt=""></a>
              <p>
                <strong>PRECISE COLOR</strong><br>
                You'll be hard-pressed to find another printer with the ability to color match across multiple
                runs so well. This means that no matter when you order you'll always have YOUR color. Remember that
                order you placed a few months back? We can match it!
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="black-title">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="column">
          <h3>BIG OR SMALL. WE PRINT THEM ALL.</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="column">
            <div class="pad-sides">
              <a href="#" class="centered-img-block"><img src="https://static.bannerstack.com/img/index-hassle-banner.jpg" alt=""></a>
            </div>
            <div class="info-teaser">
              <p>
                <strong>TYPICAL BANNER SIZES</strong><br>
                "I'll have a grande mocha cappuccino with low-fat organic creamer and sugar-free syrup."
                We can't simplify your coffee order, but we can make your banner order a lot easier. Use the
                tool below to easily pick from common sizes or create your own!
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="yellow-title">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="column">
          <h3>FIND YOUR INSPIRATION.</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="column">
            <div class="info-teaser">
              <h3 class="yellow-txt">FLAGS, POSTERS, BANNERSTANDS AND MORE!</h3>
              <p>
                <strong>POSTERS</strong><br>
                You'll be hard-pressed to find another printer with the ability to color match across multiple
                runs so well. This means that no matter when you order you'll always have YOUR color. Remember that
                order you placed a few months back? We can match it!
              </p>
              <a href="#" class="centered-img-block"><img src="https://static.bannerstack.com/img/index-framed-logo.jpg" alt=""></a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <div class="pad-sides">
              <a href="#" class="centered-img-block"><img src="https://static.bannerstack.com/img/index-banner-examples.jpg" alt=""></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="black-title">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="column">
          <h3>DESIGN. PRINT. DONE. IT'S THAT EASY!</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="column">
            <div class="info-teaser">
              <a href="#"><img src="https://static.bannerstack.com/img/index-design-computer-image.jpg" alt=""></a>
              <p>
                <strong>1. DESIGN YOUR BANNER</strong><br>
                Use any of our free fully-customizable templates to get your point across to your
                audience. Our system allows you to change colors, fonts, imagery, and even upload your
                logo! Already have your project completed? Just pick your size, quantity, and click
                upload! We'll handle the hard stuff; then we'll ship it straight to your door. Now, isn't
                that easy?
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-teaser">
              <a href="#"><img src="https://static.bannerstack.com/img/index-printing-press-image.jpg" alt=""></a>
              <p>
                <strong>2. PRINT, SHIP, HIGH-FIVE</strong><br>
                The hard part is over! Now all you have to do is tell us where it needs to go and how
                many you'd like. With our highly tearing production and logistics staff you can rest assured
                that your project will be printed at the highest quality and arrive at your door on-time and
                in perfect condition! We even offer real time tracking tools so you can always log on and
                check in!
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <div class="info-teaser">
              <a href="#" class="centered-img-block"><img src="https://static.bannerstack.com/img/index-design-print-done-1024px.jpg" alt=""></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="get-started">
      <a href="#"></a>
    </section>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') -%>

  </main>

  <%- include('../partials/final-scripts') -%>
  <script src="/js/app.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

</body>
</html>
